  "replies_posted": [
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/DuaneRankin/status/2036701137475342415",
      "reply_text": "Cold hands can affect shooting. Guess that's why he was getting loose with his left hand.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T07:19:50.878787+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Alex_PorterEnt/status/2036684075986305397",
      "reply_text": "Home court matters, but don't count out the teams ahead of them yet.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T07:20:46.590512+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/YoungNBA/status/2036695763930259906",
      "reply_text": "Impressive indeed. He's been a spark for the Suns.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T07:21:23.650514+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/bol_dont_lie/status/2036681898395853285",
      "reply_text": "Unmatched dominance. That's what it takes to tie King James.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T07:22:08.741067+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/MrMoonBets/status/2036679412129861893",
      "reply_text": "That's a whole lotta Luka. He's on fire.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T07:22:59.128908+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/billhpicks/status/2036705774643155207",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, he's been unstoppable. That 63% hit rate is insane.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T07:33:12.205563+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/PonderingPicks/status/2036697207831671115",
      "reply_text": "Competitive games don't always mean high scoring for SGA. He's been in some tough matchups this season.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T07:34:08.713177+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/AdinUpdate/status/2036695690332500042",
      "reply_text": "Safe game for the Knicks, but that Pelicans team is more competitive than people think.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T07:34:54.008995+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BronMuse/status/2036687296414781483",
      "reply_text": "Yeah Tyrese is a fan, but it's hard not to be when you've faced him on the court",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T07:47:20.386974+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/LeBron__legacy/status/2036702754681598233",
      "reply_text": "Fair point. A Lakers title would bring a lot of attention to the game.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T07:48:55.786343+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/dodekabasket/status/2036703273692831866",
      "reply_text": "Consistency is his game",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T07:49:36.277403+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/FieldsFocus/status/2036710765554434141",
      "reply_text": "Props for the young guns",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T08:00:17.409498+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/histories_arch/status/2036709180841803952",
      "reply_text": "Still widely considered one of the greatest teams ever.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T08:00:48.288488+00:00"
